'''HOON''' is the artist name of an [[Wikipedia:United States|American]] illustrator. He illustrated the [[2004]] comic ''[[Jedi: Yoda]]'', written for [[Dark Horse Comics]] by [[Jeremy Barlow]]. Hoon also drew the cover art for it, [[Knights of the Old Republic 11|''Knights of the Old Republic'' 11]], and [[Knights of the Old Republic 12|''Knights of the Old Republic'' 12]].

